Package com.tomscz.afswinx.rest.connection

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Connector
    This interface specify what must be done to create request on server.
    XMLParser
    This interface specify behavior of XMLParses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AFConnector<T>
    This class is concrete implementation of BaseConnector.
    AFSwinxConnection
    This class holds information which are necessary to get model or data and post them.
    AFSwinxConnectionPack
    This class holds all connection which are used in AFSwinx.
    BaseConnector
    This abstract class is responsible for perform requests to server.
    BaseConnector.HttpRequestBuilder
    This class is request builder.
    ConnectionParser
    This class parse connection from input file (xml) and build connection from them.
    ConnectionSecurity
    This class hold information about method, username and password.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HeaderType
    This class specify type of supported request and response types.
    HttpMethod
    This enum hold all method which can be used in connection XML specify file.
    SecurityMethod
    This enum holds all supported security method in AFSwinx.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AFSwinxConnectionException
    This is exception which is thrown during communicate with server or during creating process which leads to communication.
